{"tid":760600,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「認真求教」究竟點解咁少超級英雄改編遊戲？","createTime":"2018-07-29T16:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T01:37:59.000Z","uid":81610,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1299d7f152dc6fe1a88e3b99310e7bdfd848ad87","tid":760600,"uid":81610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"依家數得出嘅得batman spiderman 但最受歡迎嘅英雄反而冇再出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如以前有 雷神 美國隊長 iron man  hulk 都有喺xbox或者ps3上 遊戲 但嗰陣嘅英雄片點都冇依家咁高票房同知名度啦 依家marvel啲英雄電影拍咗咁多續集 證明係有市場 但所有改編遊戲都仲停留喺第一套戲嘅階段 真係好反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明明而家嘅技術係越嚟越成熟 反而哂咗啲角色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明有啲英雄好難平衡 好似超人會太屈 但你見啲英雄喺電影入面都唔係無敵啦 點都會有弱點同打唔過嘅人 點解電影做到遊戲做唔到？ <br />\n明明真係好大個市場 但冇人想做 其實係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c142bd9a5d5ca204f54c091aaee3717705c5e90","tid":760600,"uid":81610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"648ba9f620d6a662ba0d9b8c11c2680a3ae186d6","tid":760600,"uid":81610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"人嚟呀"},{"pid":"3a2881234f4f001c9127a857ff2ae46985621caa","tid":760600,"uid":81610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"89e87355dd3d4cae3bb5352e1f849c0bfe674fec","tid":760600,"uid":81610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"9f67a1dcadd7964b603b32f24315578bf6313158","tid":760600,"uid":50779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T16:18:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"843ce9d1c6a658c26ee80da608817d8e7e027fff","tid":760600,"uid":81610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f67a1dcadd7964b603b32f24315578bf6313158","tid":760600,"uid":50779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"ci